# Documentation - Vertex AI API
This is the Python Client Library (SDK) reference for the Online Predictions pre-trained API that is included with Vertex AI on Google Distributed Cloud Hosted (GDCH). Use the API to get online predictions using your custom-trained models.
For information about this API, see [Send an online prediction request](/distributed-cloud/hosted/docs/latest/gdch/application/ao-user/quickstart-op#send-an-online-prediction-request)
